descript.abstract: This dataset contains 2000 U.S. Decennial Census demographic characteristic data aggregated and/or allocated to Kansas City, Missouri neighborhoods and Kansas City, Kansas census tracts.
descript.purpose: To provide 2000 U.S. Decennial Census demographic characteristic data at an aggregate level which is meaningful to residents of Kansas City, Missouri and Kansas City, kansas.
descript.supplinf: Kansas City, Missouri data was allocated to neighborhoods based on appropriate 2000 U.S. Census Block population, housing unit, and household counts.
